## 3. Initiation Path

I don't think Pantheon has a canonical "first walk."

A new person doesn't know:

* where to begin
* what order matters
* which ideas are prerequisites
* which pieces are intentionally deferred

The graph shows everything equally.

Humans don't learn that way.

