## 4. Meta-layer

Ironically the repository demonstrates emergence but doesn't always explain its own mechanisms.

Questions I'd ask:

* Why myth instead of specification?
* Why silence?
* Why omission?
* Why recursive naming?
* Why daemons instead of modules?

Those principles seem implicit rather than explicit.

