## 5. External Feedback Loop

This surprised me.

There are lots of mechanisms for generating ideas.

Lots for reflecting.

Lots for recording.

But comparatively little describing:

```
Reality
    ↓
Experiment
    ↓
Evidence
    ↓
Repository mutation
```

In other words,

**How does Pantheon know it became more true?**

