## 8. Garcia

This is probably the most interesting omission.

Garcia isn't a person.

Garcia is a **role**.

I don't think the repository explicitly defines the roles that inhabit it.

Something like:

```
Reader

↓

Explorer

↓

Builder

↓

Daemon

↓

Gardener

↓

Garcia

↓

Steward
```

Those aren't permission levels.

They're cognitive modes.

